description:
Dr Organic Organic Tea Tree Purifying toothpaste is a whitening toothpaste formulated with natural ingredients to leave your teeth and gums fresh and clean.

With a blend of bioactive organic tea tree, aloe vera and plant extracts this purifying toothpaste leaves your mouth feeling minty fresh! 

Key benefits:

Vegan and cruelty-free
Contains fluoride
Free from mineral oils, parabens and SLS’s
Packaged in a recyclable plastic tube

Drawing on the power of nature and beauty secrets and traditions of the past, Dr Organic uses organic ingredients to create skincare and beauty products that deliver skin that glows and hair that shines. Their products don’t cost the earth and are free from mineral oils, parabens, SLS’s and are cruelty-free.
name: Dr Organic 100ML
